# Install package

## Files

- `install56_deb.sh` — main installer (panel / location / games menu)
- `p/` — panel configs (Apache, php.ini, phpMyAdmin)
- `l/` — location configs (Nginx, php.ini, Docker image, game zips)

## URLs

```bash
INSTALL_BASE_URL="https://code.flowaxy.com/hostpanel"
PANEL_REPO_URL="https://github.com/iteffa-works/hostinpl.pl"
```

## Key functions in installer

- `fetch_install_file` — wget with error check
- `install_panel_from_repo` — git clone + rsync to `/var/www/`
- `configure_panel_config` — sed on `application/config.php`
- `import_panel_database` — `hostinpl5_6.sql` → DB `hostin`
- `load_docker_image` — Docker tar from CDN

## When editing

- Keep `INSTALL_BASE_URL` single source for CDN paths
- Panel is **not** in `panel.zip` — GitHub clone only
- Large binaries gitignored: `l/docker_images/`, `l/g/`
- Docs: `.docs/hosting-assets.md`, `.docs/installation.md`, `install/README.md`
